# SCOPE TREE FORMAT — spec + example
#
# Purpose: human-reviewable intermediate before Excel generation.
# One file per project: tech-feasibility-analyses/<codename>/scope.tree
#
# Hierarchy:
#   [Module]              — top-level grouping, square brackets
#       Feature           — 4-space indent, plain text
#           Sub Feature   CMPLX  COMP  FF  PHASE  — 8-space indent + attrs
#
# Attribute abbreviations (space-separated, fixed order):
#   Complexity : XS | S | M | L | XL
#   Component  : FE (Frontend) | BE (Backend) | FS (Fullstack → writes both)
#   Form Factor: R (Responsive) | W (Web) | MN (Mobile Native) | MH (Mobile Hybrid)
#   Phase      : P1 | P2 | P3
#   #Pages     : optional integer suffix, default 3
#
# Rules:
#   - Blank line between modules (readability only, ignored by parser)
#   - Trailing spaces in attribute columns are ignored
#   - Unknown abbreviations are rejected by generate-scope-xlsx.py
#   - Comment lines start with #
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# EXAMPLE (remove before using as real input):
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

[Registration]
    Registration
        Email Signup                    XS  FE  R  P1
        Google Signup                   XS  FE  R  P2
        Linkedin Signup                 XS  FE  R  P2
        Invite-Based Registration       XS  FE  R  P3

[Identification]
    Identification
        Email Login                     XS  FE  R  P1
        Linkedin Login                  XS  FE  R  P2
        Google Login                    XS  FE  R  P2
        Session Management              XS  FE  R  P2

[First Time Experience]
    First Time Experience
        Welcome Flow                    XS  FE  R  P2
        Role & Profile Setup            XS  FE  R  P1
        Topic Preferences               XS  FE  R  P1
        First Action Nudges             XS  FE  R  P2

[Discovery]
    Discovery
        Unified Search Bar              XS  FE  R  P1
        Search Filters                  XS  FE  R  P1
        AI Semantic Search              S   FE  R  P2
        Search Suggestions              XS  FE  R  P3
        Recent Searches                 XS  FE  R  P2
    Global Search
        People to Follow                XS  FE  R  P3

[Account Profile]
    Account Profile
        Basic Profile, KPIs             XS  FE  R  P1
    User Profile
        Professional Experience         XS  FE  R  P3
